---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LegalPage from "../components/LegalPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use | LONFRO">
  <LegalPage title="Terms of Use" intro="Terms for product information, reference pricing and website inquiries.">
    <h2>Website purpose</h2>
    <p>This website is a product catalog and inquiry channel for wholesale, distribution and OEM/ODM discussions. It is not an online retail store and does not process checkout or payment.</p>
    <h2>Reference pricing</h2>
    <p>Displayed USD prices are wholesale reference prices taken from the current quotation workbook. They exclude taxes, duties, shipping and other project-specific costs. Final prices are valid only when confirmed in a formal quotation.</p>
    <h2>Product information</h2>
    <p>Specifications, colors, packing and availability may change through engineering review or production updates. Buyers should confirm all critical requirements before placing an order.</p>
    <h2>OEM and ODM projects</h2>
    <p>Customization scope, minimum quantities, development fees, tooling ownership, intellectual-property responsibilities and lead times are subject to written agreement.</p>
    <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>LONFRO names, product images and website materials may not be copied for commercial use without written permission, except where supplied to an authorized customer or distributor.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these terms can be sent to liangfen820817@gmail.com.</p>
  </LegalPage>
</BaseLayout>
